<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٤٦٨ -<span class="c5"> حديث:</span> <span class="c2">((شاهت الوجوه)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- <span class="c2">(٣/١٤٩٠)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
